<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/56774373-saul-the-heir-of-isauldur"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1532617277i/56774373._UY100_CR30,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
