<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Gollancz is doing a reprint of most of Moorcock&apos;s works. You can find it on Amazon under &quot;Elric of Melnibone and Other Stories.&quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Gollancz is doing a reprint of most of Moorcock's works. You can find it on Amazon under "Elric of Melnibone and Other Stories."<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
